<h2>Machaut: Le Lay de Confort</h2>

<dl>
<dt>Machaut: Le Lay de Confort</dt>
<dd>The Little Consort - Frans Br&uuml;ggen<br>
<i>Channel Classics 0390</i></dd>
</dl>

<h3>Contents:</h3>
<p><ol>
<li>Anon. Spain: O virgo splendens</li>
<li>Anon. England: Salve Regina</li>
<li>Anon. France: Tres doulx compains</li>
<li>Machaut: S'onques doulereusement (Le lay de confort)</li>
</ol></p>

<p>Performers: Frans Br&uuml;ggen (flute), Walter van Hauwe (flute),
Kees Boeke (flute, vielle, psaltery), Lucia Meeuwsen (soprano),
Toyohiko Satoh (mediaeval lute, cistre)</p>

<p>Playing time: 46'</p>

<p>Recording date: June 1988 (Sovana, Italy); released: 1990</p>

